  dotMask: false,
  motionBlur: 0, brightness: 0.9, 
  contrast: 1.0,
  desaturation: 0.2, 
  flicker: 0.01,
  signalLoss: 0.05
});
```  ...    Q: Can I use CRTFilter on images and videos? A: CRTFilter works on canvas elements. You can draw images or video frames  ...    © 2013-2025 CSSScript

