### J. Accessibility Guard

Every animation should be wrapped:

```css
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .scanlines::before,
  .scanlines::after,
  .glitch,
  .glitch::before,
  .glitch::after,
  .chromatic-text,
  .moving-scanline {
    animation: none !important;
  }
}
```

