### Suggested Effect Layers for the Recruitment Platform

**Global (subtle):**
- Very light scanlines overlay on the entire viewport (opacity 0.03-0.05)
- Optional: extremely subtle screen flicker (barely perceptible)

**Interactive elements:**
- Neon glow on hover for buttons and links
- Glitch effect on page transitions (title text only)
- Sound effects on interactions (like RemiliaNET's pentatonic scale approach)

**Data displays:**
- Candidate "match score" as an HP-style bar
- Profile completion as XP bar with level indicator
- Skills displayed as RPG stat chart (STR, DEX, INT, CHA mapped to hard skills, soft skills, experience, culture fit)
- Interview pipeline as dungeon map / quest stages
- Achievement badges for verified credentials

**Layout:**
- Dark theme mandatory
- Grid overlay visible in background at low opacity
- Corner bracket decorations on panels
- Section headers with red background strips (CULT.INC style)
- ALL-CAPS monospace for labels and metadata
- Mixed Japanese/English labels as accent elements

